QuestData.Title: Well, Come to the Jungle
QuestData.Description: My commander has sent me to scout for potential recruits to assist in the defense of Grom'gol Base Camp in Northern Stranglethorn. Are you familiar with Stranglethorn? It's a long way away... across the Great Sea, on the southern tip of the Eastern Kingdoms. You fit the build he was looking for... interested in leaving Kalimdor for a while?$b$bIf so, then go talk to my cohort Bort in Orgrimmar. He'll help you board the zeppelin.$b$bAnd tell him I said "Woozle wozzle." He'll know what it means.
QuestData.RewardText: Hah! That Cromula cracks me up.$b$bOh, right, Stranglethorn. You're really going?
